text: Delia Córdova was a volleyball player from Peru. Delia competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics. She was born on 30 January 1953 and died on 1 January 2016.Delia Córdova == References == Category:1953 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Peruvian volleyball players Category:Olympians for Peru Category:Sportspeople from Lima
